===Etymology===
Literally: unable to recognize the true face of [[w:Mount Lushan|Mount Lushan]]
===Idiom===
{{cmn-idiom|s|pin=bù shì lúshān zhēn miànmù|pint=bu4shi4lu2shan1zhen1mian4mu4|tra=不識廬山真面目|sim=不识庐山真面目|rs=一03}}
